# 📊 Matplotlib Projects

This folder contains implementations and examples using Matplotlib, a widely used Python library for data visualization.

---

## 📌 Contents

- Line plots  
- Bar charts  
- Histograms  
- Scatter plots  
- Pie charts  
- Customizing plots (labels, titles, colors, styles)  

---

## 🛠️ Skills Covered

- Data visualization techniques  
- Plot customization and styling  
- Creating multiple plots and subplots  
- Visual storytelling using data  

---

## 🎯 Objective

To visualize data effectively and communicate insights clearly using different types of plots and charts.

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Install Matplotlib (if not installed):

```bash
pip install matplotlib
